  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348920/extras/587bf8ac49f127178cb2234d6a1ea35f.avif?t=1681218386\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>👉 Succeed in a parkour filled with obstacles! <br>The level is very difficult! So don't lose hope... 😡<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348920/extras/5f283d97677b874c2c791e4e2d1f6c35.avif?t=1681218386\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>👉 Be careful, there is no checkpoint!<br>This means that if you fall, you have to start again! You will waste time!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348920/extras/2d522d75669b8eff8f5d894d8e776758.avif?t=1681218386\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>👉 Complete the parkours as quickly as possible and start over as few as possible! <br>👉 A death counter and a timer is available!<br><br>🤔 SO ? who will finish as soon as possible❓<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348920/extras/ddfc13ab4618f5603e728037f695ddfc.avif?t=1681218386\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Updates will be regular. Here is the program :<br><br>👉 Every month = A very big update.<br>👉 Every 2 months =  A new \"Rage pass\".<br><br>👉 Between the weeks, there will be small updates.",
